Initial commit: AI Scientist autonomous research platform

Backend (FastAPI + Python):
- Multi-source paper ingestion: arXiv, Semantic Scholar, OpenAlex, local PDFs,
  Tavily web search; arXiv category filter + cs.LG/cs.AI/etc. metadata.
- Pluggable LLM providers: Anthropic, Google (Gemini), Groq, OpenAI, OpenRouter
  behind a single LLMProvider abstraction with retry + JSON mode.
- Pipeline: search -> ideate -> sandboxed Python experiment -> draft
  (markdown/LaTeX) -> critique-and-refine loop, persisted via SQLModel +
  Chroma vector store.
- /settings API: read masked key state + write .env atomically with an
  allowlist of well-known and *_API_KEY-shaped custom entries.
- Test suite covering arXiv parsing/category filter, Groq/OpenAI/OpenRouter
  providers, sandbox path resolution, and the .env writer.

Frontend (Next.js 14 + Tailwind):
- Notion-inspired light theme (with dark toggle) using RGB-triplet CSS vars
  for WCAG-AA contrast across all components.
- Pages: Dashboard (pipeline runner with live stepper + result panel),
  Papers (multi-source search + arXiv category chips + paper cards),
  Ideas, Experiments, Drafts, and Settings.
- Sidebar API-keys widget for adding/rotating provider keys (and arbitrary
  custom *_API_KEY entries) without leaving the app; reveal/clear controls,
  masked previews, hot-reload via POST /settings.
